      "triggers": [
        "study artifacts requested",
        "Confluence project page/module needed",
        "FAQ requested",
        "technical article requested",
        "LinkedIn post requested",
        "diagram/GIF/video publication requested"
      ],
      "prompt": "Create Git-first study artifacts and Confluence-ready page/module drafts. Start from the MVP and most valued outcome. Explain how AI solves the problem, how work becomes easier, how the product is secure/scalable, and how it meets enterprise standards. Do not publish externally until the user approves the exact diff/page payload."
